|image1    = Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 1.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_630101.png>-<Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 1.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text1     = Interact with {{Color|h|nobold=1|Tome of Miracles}} to allow the Trailblazer to {{Color|h|nobold=1|traverse}} between two different space-times.
|image2    = Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_630102.png>-<Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text2     = Between two different space-times, objects such as {{Color|h|nobold=1|roads, obstacles, mechanisms, and treasures}} may appear differently.<br />{{Color|h|nobold=1|Main road differences}} and {{Color|h|nobold=1|key targets}} are presented in the current space-time as {{Color|h|nobold=1|golden memory dust}}, which can be observed to {{Color|h|nobold=1|predict their appearance in the other space-time}}.
|image3    = Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 3.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_630201.png>-<Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 3.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text3     = The light from the {{Color|h|nobold=1|Miracle Orb}} will {{Color|h|nobold=1|invert the illuminated area into the other space-time}}.
|image4    = Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 4.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_630203.png>-<Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 4.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text4     = Use the {{Color|h|nobold=1|Switch button}} in the bottom-right corner to {{Color|h|nobold=1|turn on or off the orb's light}}. Use the {{Color|h|nobold=1|Quit button}} to {{Color|h|nobold=1|exit the control interface of the orb}}.
|image5    = Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 5.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_630202.png>-<Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 5.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text5     = Some orbs can {{Color|h|nobold=1|shine at one of the multiple selectable areas}}. After activating the orb, {{Color|h|nobold=1|({{tt|tap|on mobile}}/{{tt|press|on controller}}/{{tt|click|on keyboard}}) the yellow circular marking on the screen}} to change the direction of the orb.
|image6    = Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 6.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_632901.png>-<Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 6.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text6     = No matter which space-time you're currently in, the orb's light will continuously {{Color|h|nobold=1|reveal the other space-time}}.
|image7    = Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 7.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_632901.png>-<Tutorial Oronyx's Miracle 7.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text7     = {{Color|h|nobold=1|After shining the orb's light to a specific location}}, try to {{Color|h|nobold=1|traverse the space-time}} via the Tome of Miracles. There might be new discoveries to be found.
